file.name: TaxonID.yaml
file.content:
info:
  title: BrAPI
  version: ''
openapi: 3.0.0
paths: {}
components:
  schemas:
    TaxonID:
      properties:
        sourceName:
          description: The human readable name of the taxonomy provider
          type: string
          example: NCBI
        taxonId:
          description: The identifier (name, ID, URI) of a particular taxonomy within the source provider
          type: string
          example: '2026747'
      required:
      - sourceName
      - taxonId
      type: object
